title: Salt River Bay National Historical Park and Ecological Preserve: Fees & Passes
body: Explore This Park    Plan Your Visit     Basic Information     Fees & Passes              Fees & Passes       There are no entrance fees at the park. Entrance is free. To schedule a Ranger guided tour for a group, contact Park Staff at 340-773-1460 at least two weeks in advance. Rangers will do their best to meet the request.
